summary: Sidekick of a Superstar BTS - Take 4
body:
Sidekick of a Superstar BTS - Take 4

A little bit about the writing process.

I really just want you to know how complicated it is to write this story.

First, I have these blurbs in my head, which would be only one-shots, but I’m building them into the story. They make those times, I have no information about.

Second, this story is based on real life events, so my hands are tied a bit. But that’s what makes it realistic. And what we don’t know about make my imagination come into the story. I really love a best friend Harry, but I’m sure in real life we would fall as bad as y/n did for him.

Third, the lookbook. Okay, I’m writing the story, but I have other things to do. Picking clothes for the reader and sometimes for Harry too. It’s one of my favourite parts. I love fashion.

I totally would publish this story in print with pictures and everything. I only need Harry to read the story now, to give me permission to publish it, and to give me hq photos for it.

Oh, and he really should offer me a behind the scenes tour of his concerts. Thank you! ❤
